### health
GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/health

### list all gyms
GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/gyms?city=Bengaluru

### sort by rating, women-friendly only
GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/gyms?women_friendly=true&sort=rating

### nearest gyms within 5km of Indiranagar
GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/gyms?lat=12.9716&lng=77.6412&distance_km=5&sort=distance

### filter by amenities (must have ALL)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/gyms?amenities=Sauna&amenities=AC

### full-text search
GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/gyms?q=koramangala

### price range (rupees)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/gyms?price_min=1500&price_max=2600

### gym detail
GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/gyms/cult-fit-indiranagar

### reviews (most helpful first)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/gyms/cult-fit-indiranagar/reviews?sort=helpful&limit=5

### submit an inquiry (use a real gymId from /gyms)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/inquiries
Content-Type: application/json

{ "gymId": "PASTE_UUID", "name": "Rahul S", "phone": "9876543210", "message": "Annual plan?" }

### partner demo request
POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/demo-requests
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Owner", "phone": "9876543210", "email": "o@gym.in", "gymName": "Iron House", "memberCount": "100-300" }

### register (owner)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "owner@gym.in", "password": "Passw0rd1", "fullName": "Gym Owner" }

### login
POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "owner@gym.in", "password": "Passw0rd1" }

### me (paste accessToken)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN

### owner's gyms
GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/owner/gyms
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN

